Sonar Qube?
  Code analysis tool,
  open source code quality management tool to analyze 
  Can be integrated with Maven, Ant, CI tools like Jenkins
  Rule based defect identification
  
Components?
 . A SonarQube Server
 . SonarQube Database
 . Sonar Qube plugins
 . SonarQube scanners
 
 Connect to external Database-
   $SONAR_HOME/conf/sonar.properties
  Least privilge - create tables, indices, and triggers
  
 Extensions -
   $SONAR_HOME/extensions/plugins/*.jar
   
   
 Sonar Scanner -> $SONAR_SCANNER_HOME/conf/sonar-scanner.properties define the SonarQube server to be connected to  
   
 










